function main(workbook: ExcelScript.Workbook,
	imagebase64: string = ""
)
{
	let selectedSheet = workbook.getActiveWorksheet();
	// Insert picture
	let picture = selectedSheet.addImage(imagebase64);
	// set picture position
	picture.setTop(0);
	picture.setLeft(0);
	// resize picture
	picture.setWidth(639);
	picture.setHeight(258);
}
